descriptionHtml:
This mod has 2 very strong swords in it called Sention and Xavine, Sention is craftable but not as strong and Xavine is not craftable but stronger both swords can be found somewhere in skyrim, watch the vid to see where.

- the damage is wrong xavine does 10,000 and sention does 5,000

- talk to the dark knight in dragonsreach... i dare you (its just a little joke nothing substantial happens)

----------CHANGELOG----------

fixed the bug where the weapons would fall from their place

original mod had some bugs
